Title: Mini Sink Climbing Sack
Body (HTML): ﻿The MiniSink is a bespoke Climbing bag, designed for fashion, comfort, and durability. It's not that it's only stylish; the first job of the designer is to construct a piece of material that looks great. But more importantly, the Climbing Sack is robust. That means no rips, no tears, and a backpack that you can pass down to your Grandchildren.

Title: Dover Fleece
Body (HTML):
Classic Cool.

The Dover Fleece was built for style. No question about it. But take a closer look, and you'll notice a number of touches designed for maximum durability. Made from ultrawarm fleece-lining polyester and cotton, the Dover is super-warm, and is an excellent choice for temperatures between 30-40 degrees, Fahrenheit. You can try to rip, tear, break, or scratch it, but this jacket holds up to nearly anything that comes at it. This product is best cleaned by dry-cleaning services.

Title: Leather Rucksack
Body (HTML): The Leather Rucksack is a perennial favorite for the cosmopolitan gentleman who is as adept at scaling a 50-foot boulder as he is sauntering into a coffee shop, clad in one of our stellar leather jackets. The Leather Rucksack is not only a style choice, but a practical one. It can hold 35L of stuff, which means you can fit a whole lot of groceries in it. But you can also pick in as much gear as you can, because the roll-top ensures that every single thing can fit inside. When there's a will, there's a way. But there's also our Leather Rucksack.

Title: Survival Box
Body (HTML): Our survival box is designed to fit everything you need into a small lunchbox-sized case. The SOS-can includes a fire-starter key, a multitool, a compass, tactical flashlight, and several bungee cords of various sizes. The SOS box is a necessary addition to any camping bag, and it makes a great gift for yourself or the adventure-inclined among us.

Title: BelowZero Jacket
Body (HTML):
Give 'em hell. 

We built our BelowZero Down Jacket to withstand the brutal Wisconsin winters that we grew up with in the Midwestern United States. This jacket is no exeception to our experiences, and we decided to start from scratch: first, we lined the shell with a nylon-down padding that blocks wind and keeps your core warm. On the outside, we incorporate a signature wind-proof stocking to protect against wind-chill, so you'll never be caught off guard again by what the weatherman really meant when he said "real feel."

Title: Delancey Backpack
Body (HTML):
Engineering Design. 

Precision-designed and passion-induced craftsmanship make the Delancey bag one of our staff favorites here at Allen & Lake. The Delancey Bag is designed to feel lightweight but carry a robust amount of supplies, including the most essential items necessary for your next camping trip.

Title: Condor Roll-Top
Body (HTML):
Sacrifice Nothing.

Our Condor Roll-Top is built to take nearly everything, besides the kitchen sink, with you on your trek. We built this bag out of necessity. Our conventional backpacks and handhelds simply were not cutting it anymore. After three weeks of hiking, the last thing we wanted was to worry about our bag. We solved the problem with the Condor. A precision-wrapped roll-top ensures that your stuff stays waterproof, and the leather straps add a stylish touch to the most durable bag we've ever produced.

Title: Club Glasses
Body (HTML):
Off-Trail Style. 

Our Club Glasses are modeled in a classic American style that has outlived many a redwood tree. These glasses are cool, but they're also visually prescient: the lenses offer enhanced visual acuity, and the frames are made from SolidState neohyracine lining for optimal durability.

Title: Vichy Glasses
Body (HTML):
Radical Transparency. 

We designed our Vichy Glasses for the rule breaker, the millionaire ne'er do well, and the type of person that just likes to get sh*t done. The glasses are fitted with Iridium lenses with UV400 protection, so the only thing you'll have to worry about is where your fans want their autographs signed.

Title: Brass Pocket Compass
Body (HTML):
Be Prepared. 

Our Brass Pocket Compass is a stylish accessory but also an essential one. We grew up hiking along the Rocky Mountains, and we quickly learned that your best gear is only as good as the tools you have to navigate. Our compass ensures that you'll never again struggle to interpret your map, and that the trailhead won't ever get the best of you. The compass is pressure-sealed with 180 degree thermofluid tubing, which means that it's designed to out-live almost everything besides redwoods.

Title: FiveStar Compass (GPS)
Body (HTML):
When "lost" isn't in your vocabulary.

 The FiveStar Compass is a minimal pocket-GPS tracker that provides a plethora of real-time data to help you navigate the wilderness. Included in this marine-green device is longitude, lagitude, time and date, distance from point, and home-base tracker. Once you set the FiveStar at the beginning of your hike, it will keep track of your footsteps, and it will guide you back towards the start if you ever get lost. Try it once, and you'll never hike without it again.

Title: Andromeda Shock-Proof iPhone Case
Body (HTML):
Built to last.

We built our signature phone case out of precision molded plastic, designed to withstand high temperatures and rugged conditions.

Title: Flaneur Quartz Watch
Body (HTML): We named our Quartz watch after the french word for "lounger." Flaneurs are a unique breed of gentlemen who are often found wandering into coffee shops when they're not writing novels or climbing mountains. We named the watch after this elusive breed because we wanted to create a timepiece that would align itself with the leisurely sensibilities that come after one returns to civilization after a long journey in the outdoors. The watch carries all of the features of a cosmopolitan timepiece, including an integrated day-date feature, a chromatic astrology dial, and a stopwatch designed for accuracy within 1/100th of a second. It's the perfect watch for the modern man.

Title: Tactical Flashlight
Body (HTML):
No Curfews. Ever.

Our tactical flashlight is 2000 lumens of brightness. Never worry about sundown again, and enjoy your hikes for longer periods by carrying our tactical flashlight with you. It's made from die-cast stainless steel and aluminum, so it's designed to withstand nearly anything you throw at it (or throw it at). Our design was inspired by the flashlights used by law enforcement, and so we set out to built a light that was as bright as it was durable. After countless sessions using the tactical light, we're excited to offer it to our customers.

Title: Azola Quartz Watch
Body (HTML):
The Future of Horology.

We named our Azola Quartz Watch after a genus of seven species of aquatic ferns in the family Salviniaceae. We chose this name because of the small but powerful nature of this genus type. They are extremely reduced in form and specialized, looking nothing like other typical ferns but more resembling duckweed or some mosses. Similarly, our watch looks nothing like other watches, and resembles the soft lifeforms that you're more likely to encounter in a garden than on your wrist. But we don't think that there is anything wrong with that.

Title: Marine Field Watch
Body (HTML):
Mastery. 

Our Marine Field Watch is designed for the experts in mind. The masters. This is the watch for those who seek precious timekeeping with minimal intrusions into their watch. It's the most reliable and accurate watch we've built, and it's also one of our favorites. The Marine Field Watch is set with a mechanical Quartz movement, designed for accuracy within 1/100th of a second. The day-date has been redesigned to encompass the same movement as the watch hands, which means that the replaceable cell battery is able to maintain its capacity for longer periods of time. Which means that you'll never have to worry that your clock will stop ticking. Because when the clock is ticking, the only thing at stake is everything.

Title: LED Survival Lamp
Body (HTML):
Night & Day.

Night and day. That's the difference between this headlamp and its competitors. Not only is our LED brighter, but the built in NiMH battery is designed to hold nearly twice as much juice as its closest competitor. When we built our survival lamp, our first mission was to build something bright, but not heavy enough to make carrying a burden. By using recycled plastic and a crystalline bulb lamp, our light is lighter than most other comparable pieces you've held before. And our adjustable elestic headband ensures that your most precious asset, your hands, are free for use when you need them most. *Note* This item is not available for shipping outside the United States.

Title: DoveTail Bomber
Body (HTML):
All-Day Comfort.

﻿The DoveTail Bomber is built for nearly anything. It's a versatile jacket that is just as happy in your Delancey Roll-Top bag as it is on your torso after a grueling trek up Nashua. The DoveTail is best suited towards a versatile windbreaker, and makes a great general style pick.

Title: NorthPoint Vest
Body (HTML): When tasked with constructing a warmer winter vest, we had to struggle with several constraints. Obviously, the vest needed to be warm. But it also had to be light and flexible enough to stuff into a rucksack or underneath an airplane seat. And, we needed to design it to withstand the elements. Flimsy materials weren't going to cut it. If we wanted to build a perfect vest, we had to get everything right. And yet, we did it. Here's how: a cotton-polyester down-Goose lining maintains your core temperature, while a wind-stopper outer-shell takes the edge off of the windchill. The military-grade zipper is built to function for 100,000 zips, which is probably enough for at least two lifetimes. And the lightweight construction is perfect for rolling it up into a ball for storage. We're proud of what we've accomplished with the NorthPoint, and we're excited to introduce you to this brilliant feat of engineering and product design.

Title: Handmade Cowhide Wallet
Body (HTML):
Be Bold.

When we set out to craft a high quality leather wallet, our first ambition was to use the best leather we could find. Fashioned out of South Dakota cowhide, our handmade wallet is flexible, supple, and one of our most rugged creations yet. Built for you, and built to last.
